0972a68239","tid":1625414,"uid":197258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:08:27.000Z","msg":"先唔講其他<br />\n絕對同意唔應該有反對意見就話5毛<br />\n咁樣根本冇晒討論<br />\n其實而家出去望下d post會發現連登開始分裂<br />\n就睇爆舖呢件事<br />\n支持post入面個個都支持<br />\n反對post入面就個個反對<br />\n好似平行世界咁 我只能話咁樣唔會係好事"},{"pid":"54a79b56ad5afa28447b92a552ec4ebc26865473","tid":1625414,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:12:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f25d298df47476b8d4abd95f1297111aa60b44e1","tid":1625414,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"so true<br />\npish"},{"pid":"033d8e8618e11d141a2d6a8e0d7019beaa96c2fc","tid":1625414,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RE5HPCd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRE5HPCd.jpg&h=d9d23725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時間就係金錢，裝修最緊要講效率，知道未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n孫子兵法曰：故智將務食於敵，食敵一鐘，當吾二十鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}